  "raw_html": "<main class=\"bd-main\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\">\n<div class=\"bd-content\">\n<div class=\"bd-article-container\">\n<div class=\"bd-header-article d-print-none\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items header-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items__start\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"d-print-none\">\n<ul class=\"bd-breadcrumbs\">\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item breadcrumb-home\">\n<a aria-label=\"Home\" class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../index.html\">\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-home\"></i>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../pytorch-api.html\">Reference API</a></li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../nn.html\">torch.nn</a></li>\n<li aria-current=\"page\" class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">Softmax2d</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"header-article-items__end\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"3\" data-value=\"3\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"4\" data-value=\"4\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"5\" data-value=\"5\">★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\" id=\"pytorch-article\">\n<!-- Hidden breadcrumb schema for SEO only -->\n<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../pytorch-api.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"Reference API\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"1\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../nn.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"torch.nn\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"2\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<meta content=\"Softmax2d\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"3\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\">\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"softmax2d\">\n<h1>Softmax2d<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#softmax2d\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">#</a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py class\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"torch.nn.Softmax2d\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">class</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">torch.nn.</span></span><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">Softmax2d</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">*</span></span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">args</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">**</span></span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">kwargs</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/v2.9.1/torch/nn/modules/activation.py#L1820\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch.nn.Softmax2d\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">#</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Applies SoftMax over features to each spatial location.</p>\n<p>When given an image of <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">Channels</span> <span class=\"pre\">x</span> <span class=\"pre\">Height</span> <span class=\"pre\">x</span> <span class=\"pre\">Width</span></code>, it will\napply <cite>Softmax</cite> to each location <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>s</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(Channels, h_i, w_j)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0361em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">hann</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3117em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3117em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0269em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<dl class=\"simple\">\n<dt>Shape:</dt><dd><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>Input: <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>N</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>C</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>H</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>W</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(N, C, H, W)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.08125em;\">H</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> or <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(<